## 六、API 设计

### 6.1 Platform API

| Method | Path | 描述 |
|--------|------|------|
| GET | `/api/platform/config` | 读取全局配置 |
| PUT | `/api/platform/config` | 更新全局配置（部分字段） |
| GET | `/api/platform/apps` | 列出所有 App |
| GET | `/api/platform/apps/:id` | 获取 App 详情 |
| GET | `/api/platform/skills` | 列出 Skills |
| PUT | `/api/platform/skills/:id` | 启用/禁用 Skill |
| GET | `/api/platform/memory` | 记忆查询（v0.4+） |

### 6.2 Bot Chat API（MVP 核心）

| Method | Path | 描述 |
|--------|------|------|
| POST | `/api/bot-chat/chat` | 发送消息（支持流式 SSE 响应） |
| GET | `/api/bot-chat/sessions` | 列出会话 |
| GET | `/api/bot-chat/sessions/:key` | 获取会话历史 |
| DELETE | `/api/bot-chat/sessions/:key` | 删除会话 |

#### POST /api/bot-chat/chat

**Request：**

```json
{
  "message": "你好",
  "sessionKey": "default",
  "stream": true
}
```

**Response（stream=true, SSE）：**

```
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"你好"}
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"！"}
data: {"type":"tool_use","name":"Read","args":{...}}
data: {"type":"tool_result","name":"Read","result":{...}}
data: {"type":"message_end","content":"你好！","sessionId":"..."}
```

**Response（stream=false）：**

```json
{
  "content": "你好！",
  "sessionKey": "default",
  "sessionId": "...",
  "usage": { "inputTokens": 10, "outputTokens": 5 }
}
```

### 6.3 与 Tauri 的 IPC

**Tauri 启动 Platform 进程时的握手：**

```
Tauri (Rust)                            Platform (Node.js)
  │                                            │
  │  spawn + env: AUTH_TOKEN=***               │
  │  Health check: GET /health                  │
  │ ─────────────────────────────────────────► │
  │                                            │
  │  200 OK { status: 'ok' }                    │
  │ ◄───────────────────────────────────────── │
  │                                            │
  │  API call: GET /api/platform/config        │
  │  Header: X-Desktop-Work-Token: xxx         │
  │ ─────────────────────────────────────────► │
  │                                            │
  │  200 OK { config: {...} }                   │
  │ ◄───────────────────────────────────────── │
```

**Tauri 调用 Platform 进程的 API：**

```rust
// Tauri (Rust) 示例
let response = reqwest::Client::new()
    .get("http://localhost:3737/api/platform/config")
    .header("X-Desktop-Work-Token", token)
    .send()
    .await?;
```

